<span class="displaytext">"like all americans, my thoughts and prayers are with the people of china, as they grapple with the devastation caused by the terrible earthquake which struck sichuan province earlier today. i extend my condolences to those who have lost loved ones and am especially grieved by the number of children who have been affected. i welcome president bush's offer of assistance, and join with him and all americans in our readiness to help in any way at this time of need."</span>



